title: MisterMusic Show 330 - indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 330 [2 hours] 192kbps MP3 -



New tunes on this week's show by Francisco The Man, Stars, and Minus The Bear.
Plus a big international hit from November 1976 is the 'Oldie of the Week'. 
A song that spent 3 weeks at number 1 in the US.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
